4WD Survival Guide is a completely revised and updated edition of the definitive guide to four-wheel driving. Author John Basham shares his detailed knowledge to help you deal with the multiple challenges of travelling across Australia in your four-wheel drive. Driving skills, troubleshooting and maintenance are all covered using case studies, checklists, advice, tips and cautions. This is the ebook every four-wheel driver needs before they leave home
